{"tid":1908417,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（攬抄？）不管了！放推百萬難民 土國總統：很快就會湧入歐洲","createTime":"2020-03-03T09:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T12:48:02.000Z","uid":75656,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4e41a78b344e53bf83a500b2f032e39169545a29","tid":1908417,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕因與敘利亞衝突擴大，土耳其宣布不再阻擋難民，土國總統艾爾多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）更直言，百萬難民很快就會湧入歐洲。<br />\n<br />\n為防大量敘利亞難民湧入，橫跨歐亞的土耳其自2016年負起把關責任，也讓自己成為全球收容難民數最高的國家，約有370萬人。但近日由土耳其支持的反對勢力，在敘利亞遭俄國支持的敘利亞總統阿薩德（Bashar al-Assad）政府軍空襲，造成33名軍人死亡；土國後來也擊落2架敘國戰機。<br />\n<br />\n由於三方在敘國境內的衝突瞬間升至最高，土耳其不久後便宣布開放邊境，不再管制難民進入，艾爾多安進一步表示，百萬難民很快就會湧入歐洲，批評歐盟完全沒有對安置敘國境內的難民提供幫助。<br />\n<br />\n緊鄰土耳其的希臘首當其衝，很快在兩國邊界與難民發生衝突，甚至導致一艘載滿難民的臨時船翻覆，1名兒童死亡，為土國開放邊境至今首例確認死亡案例。希臘指出，過去24小時內已經阻擋了1萬名難民。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其與歐盟在2016年達成協議，由土耳其管制難民進入，並接收希臘境內難民，土國可獲得67億美元（約新台幣2029億元）的資金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3086996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3086996&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpjHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=9346a006\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3086996&h=561e1c58\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3086996</a><br />\n<br />\n歐洲同一時間被新難民危機同支那肺炎夾撃，「極右」下次會唔會是歐洲各項選舉大勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b6bcdd17b40b86f74b2761f26e15bf4ce20ec4","tid":1908417,"uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:11:15.000Z","msg":"病毒如警鐘 - 陶傑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1907092\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1907092</a>"},{"pid":"b8d0ccd2fecabf5ade4ff9a73dba988f8b679b3a","tid":1908417,"uid":200070,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:13:36.000Z","msg":"welcome refugees <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死 垃圾EU準備永不翻身"},{"pid":"5140bfb3adb003f01fb4436cc65e84308ee13a1f","tid":1908417,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"2020年真係好世界末日feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以見證到黑警死撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c217ac821937e235287e07ce6e0ef33f26b3c111","tid":1908417,"uid":237425,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:48:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">艾爾多安進一步表示，百萬難民很快就會湧入歐洲，批評歐盟完全沒有對安置敘國境內的難民提供幫助。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">土耳其與歐盟在2016年達成協議，由土耳其管制難民進入，並接收希臘境內難民，土國可獲得67億美元</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收左錢又屈人唔幫手,狗到"},{"pid":"17e0db3989c5b264068bd1b2fe434d707cad3daf","tid":1908417,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左膠太多<br />\n歐盟自己本身經濟都唔係好好<br />\n仲要俾咁多錢應付難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540648cd704c94cdac3dab0b7288f52c63880157","tid":1908417,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯打你關歐洲咩事。。。"},{"pid":"5a437f5439847670c80f251e91158525b3133c35","tid":1908417,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:54:52.000Z","msg":"宜家要集中精神處理武漢肺炎定係難民？2020係歐盟嘅難關嚟喎"},{"pid":"37394681af8e6c595354e171e18ea0d3596a1bf8","tid":1908417,"uid":236368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540648cd704c94cdac3dab0b7288f52c63880157","tid":1908417,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯打你關歐洲咩事。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:55:37.00